All Classes

Class Description
ImageFilter
Abstract class that defines the basic ImageFilter.
ImgRaster
ImgRaster class provides the ability to store pixel values and manipulate them in a raster.
ProcessibleImage
Creates a ProcessibleImage Instance for being processed with an ImageFilter Instance.
RasterReader
RasterReader interface defines how a ImgRaster should be read from a file.
RasterTransformer
RasterTransformer interface defines how to transform a Raster image into a new filtered Raster.
RasterWriter
RasterWriter interface defines how a ImgRaster should be written to a file.
